      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Time for the cup now when TRIO (1) lands here third-up off a short break and looks well placed with his third-up record. Out to 1900m for the first time, but it doesn't look an issue on what he's done previously and Yuill should get plenty of favours from the inside gate. He looks the one to beat. SNAZZLER (4) drops right back in trip today after tiring badly over 2300m at Pinjarra. He'll be back in the run from the draw, but any sting out of the ground is a big tick for him. Can return to his best form and prove tough to hold out. DECORATION (7) is building nicely this time in work and looks ready to peak coming out in trip today. He'll appreciate any juice in the track and he has enough early speed to offset the tricky draw. Can be in this for a very long way. WHAT A PRINCE (10) is better than he's shown his past couple and looks well placed in this event. Can bounce back. SOWAR (3) won't be far away.",
